But I have no problem with the column you posted.  Supporting Bonds on
the theory that &quot;he cheated by using performance enhancing drugs, but
lots of other guys of his generation did as well&quot; has always struck me
as a legitimate POV with no lgical inconsistency or Bay Area homerism
