&quot;I didn't like the effects it had on my body,&quot; said Williams, saying he
stopped using the drug that season.

Williams said he had no knowledge that a dentist was prescribing growth
hormone for him. He said he wasn't familiar with the drug clomiphene, nor
did he comment on the steroids that were ordered. He declined to comment on
orders placed with the center after he retired.

